      <h2>The C++ executable module</h2>
      <p>One part of VCFtools is a binary executable that is written in C++ and must be compiled.
      This module can accomplish many general analyses on files of the following formats: </p>
		<ul>
			<li>VCF v4.0</li>
			<li>VCF v4.1</li>
			<li>VCF v4.2</li>
			<li>BCF v2.1</li>
		</ul>
		<p>Specific documentation can be found on the <a href="man.html">man page</a>. This page is to be used
		as a tutorial containing usage examples. 
		</p>
